item.title: Move Website from Linode to Godaddy
item.description: Working with Sach was an absolute delight. The project was a lot more complex than initially thought yet Sach went out of his way to make it happen. The project is a million miles better than I had hoped; it's mind-blowing how he has managed to create what he has done. It has all the design, function and facilities I needed and some. I did change the brief quite a bit during the design stage and I added/removed features as the site took place but Sach never complained; couldn't recommend enough!.
